dct_title_s: Israel / compiled, drawn and printed by the Survey of Israel.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, gradient tints and spot heights. Map shows international, district, and subdistrict boundaries, railways, 4 categories of roads, tracks, places of worship, and antiquities. "Copyright strictly reserved - vide Ordinance no. 16 of 1924." "Printed in June 1957." Includes sheet index
